{"tid":1530552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再入機場喇去東涌消費啦","createTime":"2019-09-02T03:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T10:58:57.000Z","uid":247463,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e88e978b6cecd007637732864edbb04389b5830e","tid":1530552,"uid":247463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"各位鍾意消費嘅巴絲<br />\n點解你地咁鍾意入機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機場最近有禁制令<br />\n入唔到去消費睇戲㗎<br />\n去東涌消費喇<br />\n都係咁正㗎<br />\n人多自然車多<br />\n咪耐心等下囉<br />\n朋友前排喺青馬大馬塞咗好耐<br />\n不過塞兩三個鐘點都入到去<br />\ngo to school by bus 嘅話<br />\n去到商場太多人最多咪排隊搭返轉頭囉<br />\n唔帶咁多隨身物品行街舒服好多<br />\n總之舒舒服服搭車睇風景都好正<br />\n放鬆吓enjoy生活啦"},{"pid":"8bc074324d680b3f70bb510db82f268ff6ded337","tid":1530552,"uid":247463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:48:51.000Z","msg":"手快開錯台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f221f2bad79157778ffa848794032475733cc3a","tid":1530552,"uid":61417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:49:05.000Z","msg":"屌，幫手推下有用post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要報平安，我要搵律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［人手置頂］被捕需知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529663</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ec29d1496180310f449d7ba0e33d8fa657f7f35a","tid":1530552,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d20435c51894aa77740e9c24c36c79b80a6954","tid":1530552,"uid":247463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f221f2bad79157778ffa848794032475733cc3a","tid":1530552,"uid":61417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"